Category
Add Category
Update Category
Delete Category
#Add Category
TIP

The following permission is needed 'category.add'

POST /api/v2/admin/category
Field	Type	Required
name_ar	String	✅
name_en	String	✅
image	File	✅
isactive	Tiny int[ 1/0 ]	*ADMIN
Output
{
    "active": false,
    "name_ar": "ABC",
    "name_en": "CBA",
    "created_at": "2021-07-01 18:11:18",
    "id": 8,
    "fullimageurl": "http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/cdn/dxoU2rRvuky3Pvn4IyakNjT2ijIleNMMtezQzmJf.png"
}
#Update Category
TIP

The following permission is needed 'category.update'

POST /api/v2/admin/category
Field	Type	Required
id	Uniq ID	✅
name_ar	String	✅
name_en	String	✅
image	File	✅
isactive	Tiny int[ 1/0 ]	*ADMIN
Output

{
    "active": false,
    "name_ar": "ABC",
    "name_en": "CBA",
    "created_at": "2021-07-01 18:11:18",
    "id": 8,
    "fullimageurl": "http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/cdn/dxoU2rRvuky3Pvn4IyakNjT2ijIleNMMtezQzmJf.png"
}
#Delete Category
TIP

The following permission is needed 'category.delete'

DELETE /api/v2/admin/category/{id}
Field	Type	Required
id	Uniq ID	✅
← Variation